OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar
OL,4,Clook
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe revamp of STV News looks good but
OL,7,Fis hardly worth the hyperbole of some
OL,8,Fclickbait articles.
OL,10,FIt is a simple evolution of the look of
OL,11,Fthe programme.
OL,13,FIts last significant visual overhaul
OL,14,Fwas 10 years ago. Time alone means it
OL,15,Fis now time to freshen things up.
OL,17,FEverything changes but everything
OL,18,Fremains the same.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
