OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar
OL,4,Clook
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe new set is still a very similar
OL,7,Fshade of blue. The signature tune has
OL,8,Fonly been remixed slightly.
OL,10,FThe format of the programme ` revised
OL,11,Flast year when dual presentation from
OL,12,Fboth Glasgow and Edinburgh ended `
OL,13,Fremains the same.
OL,15,FThe advantage of the new set is that it
OL,16,Flooks more modern and allows more space
OL,17,Ffor reporters to join the presenter.
OL,19,FBut I bet 90% of viewers will hardly
OL,20,Fnotice the changes in a couple of
OL,21,Fweeks. And this is how it should be.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
