OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar
OL,4,Clook
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe days when regional news programmes
OL,7,Fgot brand new looks every two or three
OL,8,Fyears are thankfully gone.
OL,10,FNew looks always brought complaints `
OL,11,Fsome viewers simply disliked the
OL,12,Funfamiliarity.
OL,14,FThe STV News at 6 is a successful
OL,15,Fprogramme. The challenge was to build a
OL,16,Fnew set, refresh the graphics and
OL,17,Fpotentially enhance the programme
OL,18,Fwithout annoying loyal viewers.
OL,20,FThere have been no changes to the
OL,21,Fformat.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
