OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar
OL,4,Clook
OL,5,
OL,6,FI mentioned how many regional news
OL,7,Fprogrammes used to get new looks more
OL,8,Foften than weather presenters changed
OL,9,Ftheir hairstyle.
OL,11,FBy my reckoning there were five
OL,12,Fdistinct looks for what was then
OL,13,FScotland Today between 1986 and 1996.
OL,14,FEach change brought completely new
OL,15,Ftitles, music and sets plus alterations
OL,16,Fto the format.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
