OL,4,Clook
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn contrast News at Ten stayed
OL,7,Ffundamentally unchanged from 1967 to
OL,8,F1992. Each new look kept the core
OL,9,Felements and format, simply freshening
OL,10,Fup the appearance and taking advantage
OL,11,Fof new technology.
OL,13,FThere is no suggestion of any change to
OL,14,Fthe format of STV News soon.
OL,16,FDropping the Edinburgh sub-opt would
OL,17,Fneed Ofcom approval.
OL,19,FSo would fundamental changes like an
OL,20,Fend to the separate programme for the
OL,21,Fformer Grampian region.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
